╕╨╕ 260303-03)\r\n  C:\\Dev\\menuapp-code-review\\.pipeline\\runs\\task-260316-221319-publicmenu\\prompts\\codex-reviewer.bundle.md:1600:- \r\n**╨í╨╕╨╝╨┐╤é╨╛╨╝:** Clicking \"Track Order\" on OrderConfirmationScreen briefly shows a \"╨í╤é╨╡╨╣╨║\" product popup, then returns to \r\nmenu. OrderStatusScreen never appears.\r\n> C:\\Dev\\menuapp-code-review\\.pipeline\\runs\\task-260316-221319-publicmenu\\prompts\\codex-reviewer.bundle.md:1601:- \r\n**Root cause:** `CONFIRMATION_AUTO_DISMISS_MS = 10000` (10s timer). The auto-dismiss fires `setView(\"menu\")` + \r\n`setConfirmationData(null)`, removing the full-screen confirmation overlay. A pending touch/click event from the user \r\nthen falls through to the menu grid underneath, hitting a dish card (╨í╤é╨╡╨╣╨║) which opens `DishReviewsModal`. This is a \r\nghost-click race condition on mobile.\r\n  C:\\Dev\\menuapp-code-review\\.pipeline\\runs\\task-260316-221319-publicmenu\\prompts\\codex-reviewer.bundle.md:1602:- \r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** Removed auto-dismiss timer entirely. The confirmation screen has 3 explicit navigation buttons (back to \r\nmenu, my orders, track order) ΓÇö auto-dismiss is unnecessary and harmful. Removed `CONFIRMATION_AUTO_DISMISS_MS` \r\nconstant, `confirmationTimerRef` ref, all timer setup/cleanup code.\r\n  C:\\Dev\\menuapp-code-review\\.pipeline\\runs\\task-260316-221319-publicmenu\\prompts\\codex-reviewer.bundle.md:1603:- \r\n**╨ñ╨░╨╣╨╗:** `x.jsx` (PublicMenu main page)\r\n  C:\\Dev\\menuapp-code-review\\.pipeline\\runs\\task-260316-221319-publicmenu\\prompts\\codex-reviewer.bundle.md:1604:- \r\n**RELEASE:** `260303-04 x RELEASE.jsx`\r\n\r\n\r\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
